{
  "texts": [
    "In this sense, it could be argued that the AIA seeks to balance innovation with ethical considerations.",
    "Nevertheless, complex challenges remain in terms of enforceability, democratic legitimacy, and futureproofing.",
    "The implementation of the AI Act will face many challenges, particularly in terms of enforcement and governance.",
    "The establishment of the AI Office, together with the European Artificial Intelligence Board, is essential to provide the necessary expertise and coordination between member states.",
    "Effective enforcement will depend on the ability to harmonise the different regulatory landscapes across the EU and ensure consistent application of the rules."
  ]
}